Install brew
Install Node with brew
Use Visual Studio Code as IDE - optional recommendation
Install Cypress via VSC (Install in the same folder as the Test Code)

- Create a package json (similar to maven or nugget)
-- npm init -y
- Install Cypress
-- npm install cypress@3
- Open Cypress
-- npx cypress open
